Class GOST3411_2012Digest

  • java.lang.Object

    public abstract class GOST3411_2012Digest
extends java.lang.Object
implements ExtendedDigest, Memoable
    Base class for GOST3411-2012 256-bit and GOST3411-2012 512-bit digests.
